item.title: Walking Audit - POSTPONED
item.description: For our April “meeting” we had planned a Walking Audit   conducted by an experienced representative from Wellmark’s Healthy Hometown   initiative. Due to weather concerns this event has been POSTPONED to Thursday, May 5 at 5 PM. Everyone is invited to attend and walk together! We will have a regular meeting at the Wieting, 5 PM, April 7, instead of the Walking Audit and that meeting agenda is available here .
